text: Lycée Franco-Hondurien (LFH; ) is a French international school in Tegucigalpa, Honduras."Locaux" (Archive)/"Nuestra Ubicación" (Archive). Lycée Franco-Hondurien. Retrieved on March 23, 2015. "residencial Las Colinas boulevard Francia Apartado Postal 3743 Tegucigalpa, Francisco Morazan Honduras" It serves levels maternelle (preschool) through lycée (senior high school).
